data.title: Walnutport, PA
data.meta_description: Official website of Becky's Drive-In Movie Theatre, Walnutport, PA
data.text:
Area Cub Scouts and their families are invited to watch the double features on Screen 1 and camp out overnight after the movies. Each scout will receive a patch and enjoy free rides on our trackless train, trackless fire engine, and moon bounce during the evening.

More information, including the features, will be announced soon!

Area Girl Scouts and their families are invited to enjoy a double feature on Screen 1 and camp out overnight after the movies. Each scout will receive a patch and enjoy free rides on our trackless train, trackless fire engine, and moon bounce.

More information - including the movie selection - will be announced at a later date.
